<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Climate Solutions</title>
    <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/navbar', { page: '/' }) %>  <!-- Include navbar -->

    <nav class="navbar bg-base-100">
        <div class="flex-1">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-ghost normal-case text-xl">Climate Solutions</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-none">
            <ul class="menu menu-horizontal p-0">
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li tabindex="0" class="dropdown">
                    <!-- Updated to use dropdown -->
                    <label tabindex="0" class="btn btn-ghost">Sector</label>
                    <ul tabindex="0" class="dropdown-content menu p-2 shadow bg-base-100 rounded-box w-52">
                        <li><a href="/solutions/projects?sector=agriculture">Agriculture</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/solutions/projects?sector=industry">Industry</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/solutions/projects?sector=energy">Energy</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="hero min-h-screen bg-base-200">
            <div class="hero-content text-center">
                <div class="max-w-md">
                    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">This is about my Projects</h1>
                    <p class="py-6">Discover innovative climate solutions that aim to make the world a better place.</p>
                    <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary">View Projects</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Project Cards Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                    <img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_farmlandrestoration01.jpg" alt="Project 1 Image"/>
                    
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Abandoned Farmland Restoration</h2>
                    <p>Restoration can bring degraded farmland back into productivity and sequester carbon in the process.</p>
                    <a href="/solutions/projects/1" class="btn btn-primary">More Information</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_alternativecement02.jpg" alt="Project 2 Image"/></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Alternative Cement</h2>
                    <p>Conventional cement production is a significant source of carbon dioxide. Reformulation can reduce emissions by millions of metric tons each year.</p>
                    <a href="/solutions/projects/2" class="btn btn-primary">More Information</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_biomass01.jpg" alt="Project 3 Image"/></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure</h2>
                    <p>Infrastructure is essential for supporting safe and abundant bicycle use, which curbs emissions by reducing the need for fossil-fuel-dependent transportation.</p>
                    <a href="/solutions/projects/3" class="btn btn-primary">More Information</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
